        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A French airliner produced in 1925. A fourengined biplane developed from the Bleriot 115 and 135 but larger than these. Two were built for Air Union (the Paris-London route). Both crashed with fatalaties in 1926 (Kent).</skos:scopeNote>
