        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A building or group of buildings containing equipment capable of transmitting and receiving radio signals. Use BROADCASTING RADIO STATION for broadcasting establishments e.g. BFBS Radio stations.</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
