        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">An often squat building with thick, loopholed walls and a flat roof, designed to accommodate a variety of weapons, usually strategically positioned to cover a vulnerable point in a defensive system.</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
    </skos:broader>
