    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">Single-engined fighter, developed from the Camel. Entered service in 1918 and became the RAF's first mainstay peacetime fighter.</skos:scopeNote>
    <dcterms:publisher rdf:resource="http://www.historicengland.org.uk"/>
